Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • Matrix
  • public class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing a mathematical matrix and providing linear algebra operations. This class supports various matrix operations including addition, multiplication, row reduction, eigenvalue computation, and solving systems of linear equations.
